title: Drawing, Design for Sideboard "C" with Six Legs and Five Drawers, 1900–05
title_raw: Design for Sideboard "C" with Six Legs and Five Drawers
inscribed: Inscribed in graphite lower right corner: SIDEBOARD 'C', and at upper left of design: [numerical notations indicating dimensions]
creditline: Gift of The Lake St. Louis Historical Society
description: Rectangular sideboard on six fluted straight tapering legs; tripartide front has convex central section containing five drawers - two horizontal drawers flanked by a single vertical drawer on each side and topped by single horizontal drawer with pair of round pulls; low backsplash.

participants.person_name: The Lake St. Louis Historical Society

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, Design for Sideboard "C" with Six Legs and Five Drawers, 1900–05. Graphite on thin cream paper. 
Gift of The Lake St. Louis Historical Society. 2000-69-22
